{"tid":1481084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪覺得好多POST好亂？驚帶風向？一次過同你總結晒今日既POST！","createTime":"2019-08-17T14:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:41:15.000Z","uid":41355,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b710e21ceba06d27b5850e03c818d9d8d58301","tid":1481084,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">／行動篇</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一句講哂，818黑衫定彩虹戰衣 (3600票黑衫； 80票彩虹)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1478100/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1478100/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一句講曬，為左香港818準時一次，得唔得？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1480801/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1480801/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">聽日理論上未係遊行，暫時目標係要集會坐爆港島<br />\n集會唔需要你分流比人向前遊行，只需要同一時間坐爆個地方，甚至係成個港島，畫面先最震撼</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>仲諗緊聽日點解唔勇武嘅同我入曬嚟 (2030正評； 6０負評)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479887/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479887/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">818盡力和平 其實係一種勇<br />\n和平其實係一種好撚有力量嘅信念<br />\n可以令到真正嘅暴力浮面<br />\n無得再用指責我地暴力做遮醜布<br />\n黑警集團就會孭返背後嘅巨大壓力</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔關勇唔勇武 818全部都要帶裝自保  狗一定好大機會清場  (1560正評； 6０負評)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1475555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1475555</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>岑敖暉：818 一定一定一定要full gear (910正評； 60負評)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479688/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479688/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">我心底也非常渴望818是純和理非。現在實在要一場純和理非的遊行和集會，對上一次全港超大型的集會示威，已經是616。<br />\n但，還是一定要full gear、著黑衫。<br />\n大佬，我不想再見到有義士放煙時除個豬嘴俾無裝備的弱勢人士，而自己一路跑一路吸入成肺毒氣的情景呀。自己準備好基本的裝備，不但是保護自己，也是在保護身邊的朋友呀。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>講定先，聽日遊行完最好立即散水 (5400正評； 190負評)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479736/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479736/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">聽日共識係和理非<br />\n完咗就散水先係正確做法</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>王丹：如果中共真的派武警進入香港怎麼辦？</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476145/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476145/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">番屋企瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7bc95d0fa703552bf9dc2504dc19a378ed2e1cda","tid":1481084,"uid":41355,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">／文宣篇</span><br />\n<br />\n【香港：緊急狀態】Hong Kong: The clock is ticking<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YSUtmDHOIPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYSUtmDHOIPI&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1NB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=91edd99e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YSUtmDHOIPI</a><br />\n<br />\n［由6.9到今日］ HONG KONG 2019, SUMMER<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsjiZD2E6h0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCsjiZD2E6h0&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1NB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=5d6bac62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CsjiZD2E6h0</a><br />\n<br />\n外國人心聲︰得喇我知香港喇，咁我可以點幫手呀大佬？你講至得架！點幫呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1472787/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1472787/</a><br />\n<br />\n[肯離開同溫層未] 成個Twitter都係五毛大軍洗版 一齊反擊Twitter！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479651/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479651/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【民心】睇吓外媒頭版點報機場事件先啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471174/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471174/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">．示威者一邊向受影響旅客道歉，一邊用行李車堵塞離境大堂。<br />\n．事件升溫的原因是一位來自大陸的卧底公安<br />\n．香港警察為左解救公安，身穿防暴裝入機場揮警棍打示威者。<br />\n．示威者為解救被捕女士，攻擊警察，警察舉槍。</span><br />\n<br />\n劉亦菲呢單野真係要響美國煲大佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476570/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476570/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發文宣計劃】首個針對中立淺藍黃嘅大型文宣「牆紙」上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6e0332d7788cf64def3c1a4e42b2fa3725b9fecd","tid":1481084,"uid":41355,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">／資訊篇</span><br />\n<br />\n[新的合作模式] 大家唔好再標籤自己係「和理非」或者「勇武」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1480087/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1480087/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警即日起將強行闖入所有私人地方<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479668/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479668/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[四兩撥千斤]就高永文彈珠射爆3M眼罩論投訴美國3M做假<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479670/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n搞清楚鬼既運作之後，你就明白點解唔需要捉鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1480035/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1480035/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【和理非升級】８２３人鏈籌備召集！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480152</a><br />\n<br />\n以後邊個想屌人、互屌、對自己人有不滿，就望住呢堆相 睇下呢堆片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471935/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471935/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5f3c1cbf636d258791e5c9d3f28385682f076d2e","tid":1481084,"uid":144942,"like":